column3: Nahi, sirf security staff aur police hi CCTV footage dekh sakti hai.

column2: Agar 2 log ek hi cheez claim karein to kya hota hai?
column3: Staff ownership ka saboot mangega aur aakhri faisla investigation ke baad hoga.

column2: Mera passport foreign national ka hai, kya alag procedure hoga?
column3: Nahi, procedure sab ke liye same hai. Aapko apni embassy ko bhi inform karna chahiye.

column2: Main ne samaan milne ke baad report cancel karani hai, kaise karun?
column3: Aap usi counter pe ja kar inform kar dein jahan report likhwai thi.

column2: Airport ke bahar parking area mein samaan ghum ho jaye to kahan report karein?
column3: Parking management aur airport security dono ko inform karein.

column2: Mere bag mein khanay peenay ki cheezein thi, kya wo kharab ho jayengi?
column3: Haan, aisi cheezein jald hi zaye kar di jati hain.

column2: Kya airport ki mobile app se lost item report ho sakta hai?
column3: Filhal ye sahulat dastyab nahi, aapko counter pe hi aana hoga.

column2: Mujhe ek laawaris (unattended) bag mila hai, mujhe kya karna chahiye?
column3: Bag ko na chhuein aur forun airport security staff ko bulayein.

column2: Kya connecting flight ke doran ghumay samaan ki report yahan ho sakti hai?
column3: Haan, aap yahan report kar sakte hain, wo aapki final destination airport se coordinate kar lenge.

column2: Jewellery ke liye kya koi special security hoti hai?
column3: Haan, qeemti samaan ko aam tor par aleda mehfooz locker mein rakha jata hai.

column2: Mujhe apna bag toota hua mila hai, kya iski report Lost & Found mein hogi?
column3: Nahi, toote hue samaan ki report airline ke baggage services counter par hoti hai.

column2: Kya Lost & Found ka data online public hota hai?
column3: Nahi, security ki wajah se ye data public nahi kiya jata.

column2: Agar main authorization letter na de sakun to kya mera dost samaan le sakta hai?
column3: Nahi, baghair authorization letter aur ID ke samaan kisi aur ko nahi diya jata.

column2: Main wheelchair par tha aur mera samaan ghum gaya, kya koi madad karega?
column3: Haan, special assistance staff aur Lost & Found aapki puri madad karenge.

column2: Mere credit cards wallet ke andar thay jo ghum gaya hai, forun kya karun?
column3: Forun apne bank ko call karke tamam cards block karwayein aur phir report karein.

column2: Kya report file karne ke liye boarding pass dikhana zaroori hai?
column3: Haan, flight details confirm karne ke liye boarding pass ya ticket ki copy zaroori hoti hai.

column2: Saman claim karte waqt kya original CNIC dikhana parta hai?
column3: Haan, shanakht ke liye original CNIC ya passport dikhana lazmi hai.

column2: Kya main phone call par apne samaan ki shanakht kar sakta hun?
column3: Behtar hai ke aap khud aakar shanakht karein, lekin kuch cases mein photo se ho jati hai.

column2: Mere bachay ka school bag reh gaya hai, usmein kitabein hain.
column3: Aap Lost & Found mein report karwayein, aisi cheezein aksar mil jati hain.

column2: Agar Lost & Found counter band ho to kya karein?
column3: Aam tor par ye 24 ghante khula rehta hai, agar nahi to airport information desk se pata karein.

column2: Mujhe mera ghumshuda samaan mil gaya hai, kya koi form sign karna hoga?
column3: Haan, aapko samaan wasool karne ki receiving deni hogi.

column2: Airport Masjid mein meri topi (cap) reh gayi, kahan milegi?
column3: Aap Masjid ke intezamia aur airport Lost & Found dono se pooch sakte hain.

column2: Kya security check ke dauran tray mein rakha samaan ghum ho sakta hai?
column3: Haan, ho sakta hai. Aap forun wahan mojood security staff ko batayein.

column2: Domestic aur international flights ka Lost & Found ek hi hai?
column3: Aam tor par ek hi hota hai, lekin bade airports par alag bhi ho sakta hai.

column2: Kya live animals (pet) ke ghum hone par bhi Lost & Found report letay hain?
column3: Haan, aap forun report karein, iske liye special teams hoti hain.

column2: Mujhe 10 din ho gaye hain, samaan nahi mila, ab kya koi umeed hai?
column3: Aap apne complaint number se status check karte rahein, kabhi kabhi waqt lag jata hai.

column2: Agar bag ke andar koi aisi cheez ho jo illegal ho to kya hoga?
column3: Aisi soorat mein airport security qanooni karwai kar sakti hai.

column2: Kya main whatsapp video call par samaan ki shanakht kar sakta hun?
column3: Nahi, aam tor par iski ijazat nahi hoti. Aapko email par photo bhejni hogi.

column2: Main ne samaan ki report late karwai, kya is se koi masla hoga?
column3: Behtar hai jald report karwayein, lekin late report bhi darj ki jati hai.

column2: Mera electronic saman (e.g. drone) mila hai, kya uski battery nikaal di jayegi?
column3: Haan, hifazat ke tehat aam tor par electronic items se batteries nikaal di jati hain.

column2: Ghumshuda samaan ke liye claim ka process kitna lamba hota hai?
column3: Agar samaan mojood ho to shanakht ke baad forun mil jata hai, warna talash mein waqt lagta hai.

column2: Maine boarding gate pe apna neck pillow chhor diya, kya karun?
column3: Boarding staff ya Lost & Found counter se rabta karein.

column2: Kya samaan milne par koi delivery charges hain?
column3: Agar airline home delivery kar rahi hai to unki policy ke mutabiq charges ho sakte hain.

column2: Mera bag ajeeb (weird) shakal ka tha, kya main tasveer dikha sakta hun?
column3: Haan, bilkul. Tasveer se aapka samaan dhoondne mein aasani hogi.

column2: Food court mein mera khane ka parcel reh gaya, kahan milega?
column3: Food court management aur Lost & Found counter, dono jagah maloom karein.
